@startuml UC_자료실
!theme plain
left to right direction
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

title 자료실/커리큘럼 유스케이스

actor "스터디원" as member
actor "스터디장" as leader

rectangle "자료실" {
    usecase "자료 목록 조회" as UC1
    usecase "자료 상세 조회" as UC2
    usecase "자료 업로드" as UC3
    usecase "사진 촬영 업로드" as UC4
    usecase "자료 댓글 작성" as UC5
    usecase "자료 삭제" as UC6
}

rectangle "커리큘럼" {
    usecase "커리큘럼 조회" as UC10
    usecase "커리큘럼 생성/수정" as UC11
    usecase "진도 체크" as UC12
    usecase "진도 현황 조회" as UC13
}

' 스터디원
member --> UC1
member --> UC2
member --> UC3
member --> UC4
member --> UC5
member --> UC10
member --> UC12
member --> UC13

' 스터디장
leader --> UC6
leader --> UC11

note right of UC3
  링크/파일/이미지/동영상
  업로드 가능
end note

note right of UC4
  모바일에서 카메라로
  바로 촬영하여 업로드
end note

note right of UC13
  멤버별 주차별
  진도 현황 대시보드
end note

@enduml
